Kapanpun kamu membutuhkan bantuan,

00:33:58.220 --> 00:33:59.340
beritahu aku.

00:34:21.740 --> 00:34:22.580
Tuan Muda,

00:34:22.900 --> 00:34:23.940
Kemana kita akan pergi?

